description:
If you've missed Guyladriel girlbossing her way through enemy armies, then wait no longer because Rings of Power episode 4 has you covered. Also, we laugh as Concord, Sony's $100 Million flagship game crashes and burns in barely a week. And Terminator Zero turned out to be surprisingly good. Join me, MauLer, Space Ice, Nerdrotic, Grummz and Echo Chamberlain as we discuss it all. 

Subscribe to Space Ice: https://www.youtube.com/@SpaceIce
Subscribe to Nerdrotic: https://www.youtube.com/@nerdrotic
Subscribe to Echo: https://www.youtube.com/@EchoChamberlain
title: Open Bar #110 - Galadriel Girlbosses Again, Concord Crashes, Terminator Zero
